text: William Arthur Land was an English track and field athlete. ==Athletics career== Land was the 1932 high jump AAA champion He competed in the discus throw and high jump at the 1934 British Empire Games.Land also held the British javelin throw record in 1935. ==References== Category:English male high jumpers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1934 British Empire Games Category:English male discus throwers Category:English male javelin throwers
